headline.print_headline: EU's Barroso Condemns Russian Incursion in Call With Putin
headline.main: EU's Barroso Condemns Russian Incursion in Call With Putin

lead_paragraph: European Commission President Jose Manuel Barroso condemned "significant incursions" by Russian forces into Ukraine in a phone call with Russian President Vladimir Putin on Friday, the EU said.
